                <head>No. 139<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No reply was ever received by the three Western Powers in response to their note
                    of September 23. However, the questions of a German peace treaty, German unity,
                    and all-German elections continued to be considered by policymakers in the
                    Department of State. For further documentation on these questions, see <ref
                        target="#d140">Documents 140</ref> ff. and <ref target="#d257">257</ref>
                    ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
